            "heading": "ONLINE CUSTOMER SERVICE (HA NOI)",
            "font_body": true,
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p><strong>JOB DESCRIPTION</strong></p><ul><li>Receive and advise customers on SEESON's online sales channels</li><li>Monitor and process online orders</li><li>Receive inquiries, assist in answering and resolving customer complaints</li><li>Perform other tasks as assigned by the supervisor/manager</li></ul><p><strong>REQUIREMENTS</strong></p><ul><li>Female preferred, age: 18-21 years old</li><li>Currently studying at universities in Hanoi</li><li>Cheerful, enthusiastic, eager to learn personality</li><li>Good communication, problem-solving, and quick situational handling skills</li><li>Honest and responsible in work</li><li>Good conversational English</li></ul><p><strong>BENEFITS</strong></p><ul><li>Basic salary + sales commission</li><li>13th-month salary</li><li>Training & development opportunities</li><li>Young, dynamic work environment</li><li>Employee purchase discounts</li><li>Gifts for holidays such as Lunar New Year, International Women's Day, National Day, Mid-Autumn Festival, birthday, etc.</li><li>Annual team building</li></ul><p><strong>WORK LOCATION</strong></p><ul><li>19-21 Yen Ninh Alley, Ba Dinh District, Hanoi</li></ul><p><strong>WORKING HOURS</strong></p><ul><li>Shift work:</li><li>Morning shift: 8:30 AM - 1:00 PM</li><li>Afternoon shift: 1:00 PM - 5:30 PM</li><li>Evening shift: 5:30 PM - 10:00 PM</li></ul><p><strong>HOW TO APPLY</strong></p><ul><li>Interested candidates please send your CV to the email address: <a href=\"mailto:retail.hr@seeson.vn\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"mailto:retail.hr@seeson.vn\"><em>retail.hr@seeson.vn</em></a></li><li>Candidates who pass the resume screening round will be contacted for an interview.</li></ul><p><strong>Note:</strong></p><ul><li>Email subject should be: <em><strong>[ONLINE CS] - Full name</strong></em></li><li>CV must include a portrait photo taken within the last 6 months</li></ul>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_NXPVAV": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "PRODUCT QUALITY CONTROL (HA NOI)",
            "font_body": true,
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p><strong>JOB DESCRIPTION</strong></p><ul><li>Inspect finished products to ensure they are defect-free and meet quality standards.</li><li>Sort products into standard/non-standard categories.</li><li>Identify and address defects that arise in products.</li><li>Clean and package products after the quality inspection process is complete.</li></ul><p><strong>REQUIREMENTS</strong></p><ul><li>Female preferred, age: 18-21 years old</li><li>Currently studying at universities/colleges in Hanoi</li><li>Honest and responsible at work</li><li>Careful, meticulous, with good observation skills</li></ul><p><strong>BENEFITS</strong></p><ul><li>Salary: 25,500 VND/hour</li><li>Bonuses on holidays and Tet throughout the year</li><li>Trained in a professional environment</li><li>Young and dynamic working environment</li><li>Entitled to employee purchase discount policies</li><li>Gifts for holidays, International Women's Day, National Day, Mid-Autumn Festival, birthdays, etc.</li></ul><p><strong>WORK LOCATION</strong></p><ul><li>44 Ton Duc Thang, O Cho Dua Ward, Hanoi City</li></ul><p><strong>WORKING HOURS</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum 4.5 hours/shift, 6 shifts/week</li><li>Flexible shift registration weekly</li></ul><p><strong>HOW TO APPLY</strong></p><p>Interested candidates please send your CV to the email address: <em><strong>retail.hr@seeson.vn</strong></em></p><p>Candidates who pass the resume screening round will be contacted for an interview.</p><p><em>Note:</em></p><ul><li>Email subject should be: <em><strong>[QUALITY CONTROL] - Full Name</strong></em></li><li>CV must include a portrait photo taken within the last 6 months</li></ul>",
